SearchLineEdit v0.1

LineEdit and SearchLineEdit are enhanced QLineEdit widgets for inputting text.

LineEdit inherits from QLineEdit and implements the following
additional functionalities: an inactiveText (displayed a grayed-out
hinting text as long as the user didn't enter any text),
ability to set widgets both on left and rigth side.

SearchLineEdit inherits from LineEdit and implements the following
additional functionalities: animated clear button and custom menu button.
